query:
INSERT INTO
            community_tier_list_entries(character, eidolon, average, variance, votes, total_votes)
        VALUES
            ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
        ON CONFLICT
            (character, eidolon)
        DO UPDATE SET
            average = EXCLUDED.average,
            variance = EXCLUDED.variance,
            votes = EXCLUDED.votes,
            total_votes = EXCLUDED.total_votes
